Interface ProxyTimeZone

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Proxy
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    ProxyInstant

    public interface ProxyTimeZone
extends Proxy
    Interface to be implemented to mimic guest language objects that represents timezones.
